metadata.name: Hands On | NFT #1
metadata.description: Hands On | NFT is a collaborative platform for brands and artists alike. Hands On partners with upcoming and professional brands to educate and promote to our community. The Hands On | NFT website will be an inclusive community dedicated to the further growth of crypto, real estate, and media. Hands On focuses on bringing a positive impact to the world around us, this will include special collections that will be donated to specific causes. For example, the proceeds of our first special collection of 300 Ukrainian Keys will 100% be donated to a fund helping the cause.
